snippet.title: Mnemonic Devices trailer
snippet.description:
Your memory is gone, but at least the voice in your head seems to know what's going on. 

Mnemonic Devices, a visual novel for NaNoRenO2019. Watch memories of the past to help decide the future.

Link: https://minyan.itch.io/mnemonic-devices

Stats: 
Two love interests
Genre: Sci-fi/Romance
Warnings: Strong language, alcohol use, suggestive scenes, descriptions of sexual situations
Team:
Project leader, sprites, writing, UI: Minyan (https://minyan.itch.io/) 
CGs: Kyan (https://jkyan.itch.io/)
BGs: Reikun (https://skyharborr.itch.io/)
Composer, Sound Designer: Ray (https://itch.io/profile/julianraystudio)
Editing: Wray, Zatomi
Testing: Clumsy, Averxy
